    "together with the condition that ξ (the physical radial distance of the apparent images on the observer's sky) is larger than the solar radius.",
    "What if the Sun were transparent, or we were looking for strongly-lensed neutrinos?",
    "Then the requirement that ξ is more than the solar radius would be lifted, and the condition (9) would apply as",
